_refine.details
;ALL NON-BONDED INTERACTIONS WERE REMOVED BETWEEN THE
ACTIVE SITE NICKEL IONS AND NICKEL-BOUND WATERS 500, 501, 502.
THE OCCUPANCIES FOR ACTIVE SITE WATERS HOH 500 - HOH 502
WERE REFINED WITH A FIXED B-FACTOR OF 20 ANGSTROMS**2.
THE REFINED OCCUPANCIES FOR THESE WATERS SUGGEST NEARLY
FULL OCCUPANCY FOR EACH OF THEM, ALTHOUGH THEY ARE
POSITIONED TOO CLOSE (~ 2.0 ANGSTROMS APART) FOR
SIMULTANEOUS OCCUPANCY.

THE OCCUPANCIES FOR ACTIVE SITE WATERS HOH 500 - HOH 502
WERE REFINED WITH A FIXED B-FACTOR OF 20 ANGSTROMS**2.
THE REFINED OCCUPANCIES FOR THESE WATERS SUGGEST NEARLY
FULL OCCUPANCY FOR EACH OF THEM, ALTHOUGH THEY ARE
POSITIONED TOO CLOSE (~ 2.0 ANGSTROMS APART) FOR
SIMULTANEOUS OCCUPANCY.
;
